Input Parameters\:
seconds - the number of seconds to sleep

Responses\:

If a boolean operation, it evaluated to true. failure - Something went wrong or the boolean operation returned false. 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.c7fd10d2-804d-443b-ba3e-f6da1a5c3f30.transition.description=The specified amount of time has not yet elapsed, continue looping. 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.d2be2999-1d13-4fd3-94b1-5a042df7610e.transition.description=average was below threshold. 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.d334dd7e-2043-4156-87b3-e51509c61588.description=start time cleared from global context. 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.d68e018c-0155-4417-a21b-9c058e7c959b.description=Saves average to global context. 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.description=Loops over a specified amount of time and averages a value fed into it over this time. Checks to see if this value is above or below a specified threshold. This flow should only be used as a subflow since using it on its own will always return the continue response unless runLength is assigned a value of 0. When this flow gives the continue response the calling flow must obtain another value, and pass it to this flow again. inputs\: runLength - the number of seconds this flow should loop. waitTime - the number of seconds this flow should before returning when looping. threshold - A value to compare the averaged value to. VALUE - the value of the most recent function call, which will be added to the average. keyName - the key that the list of values will be stored in until averaging. responses\: less than - The average was less than the threshold. equal - the average was the same as the threshold. greater than - the average was greater than the threshold. Continue - the specified amount of time has not yet passed, the calling flow should run another operation and pass this flow another value. failure - values in keyName could not be averaged. additional results\: average - the average value of the list. only a result is the response is success. List - a list that is accumulating values. This is erased when the time runs out. timeStarted - the time since you made the first function call. this is erased when time runs out. 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.ebb3894c-9515-4f31-8eff-51e1250529cf.transition.description=average was greater than threshold. 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.f95a4fc3-59d4-408c-b604-87b78e87b92e.transition.description=List saved to global context 0e37b1a1-ba19-4d4a-820c-294ad4f56147.fbbfbba9-6917-4b4b-9dd6-cb5b0758028c.description=Performs a mathmatical operation on two numbers Inputs\: operation - The operation to perform. value1 - the first value. value2 - the second value. Returns\: The result of the operation, for boolean values this is true or false. Responses\: success - The operation completed successfully.
